# 'use client' directive

- `'use client'` is allowed only in `.component.tsx` / `.context.tsx` files that actually need state, effects, event handlers, or browser APIs.
- Never add it to `.hook.ts`, `.util.ts`, `.types.ts`, or `.constants.ts` files.
- Prefer server components when no interactivity is needed.
